Groupon May Expand ‘Groupon Now’ Service If U.S. Tests Go Well, CEO Says

-- B y   J u n   Y a n g
-- 
2011-06-07T03:24:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-07/groupon-may-expand-groupon-now-service-if-u-s-tests-go-well-ceo-says.html
Groupon Inc., owner of the world’s
largest online coupon site, may expand its “Groupon Now”
service globally if tests in the U.S. go well, Chief Executive
Officer  Andrew Mason  said at a press briefing in  Seoul .  To contact the reporter on this story:
